{"updated": 1433599464000, "content": "Hey Foodies,<br /><br />This Sambharo or Achar or Condiment is given with all kinds of Fried food.. Whether its Fafda, Kachori, Samosa, anything! I've seen this being given even with Vada Pav!<br /><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\" wp-image-1310 aligncenter\" src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/cscom-2019.appspot.com/o/content%2F2014%2F03%2F12.jpg?alt=media\" alt=\"1\" width=\"691\" height=\"389\" /></p><br />With subtle changes, This just tastes awesome with anything! Now, like for a spicy fried food, cut the spice in this with lemon.. And so on.. So, why not lets make some now!<br /><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\" wp-image-1311 aligncenter\" src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/cscom-2019.appspot.com/o/content%2F2014%2F03%2F31.jpg?alt=media\" alt=\"3\" width=\"691\" height=\"389\" /></p><br /><br /></div><br /><br />Spend 2 mins to make this and enjoy your favorite fried food in next level! The perfect balance of sweet, sour, spice and that extra kick of mustard does wonders!<br /><br /><br /><br />That\u2019s it for today, Hope to hear from you soon <img src=\"https://cookingshooking.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif\" alt=\":)\" /><br /><br />Thanks for stopping by,<br /><br />CookingShooking is on <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/CookingShooking\">YouTube</a>, <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/CookingShooking\">Facebook</a>, <a href=\"https://cookingshooking.com/cabbage-sambharo/www.Google.com/+CookingshookingIn\">Google+</a>, <a href=\"http://twitter.com/CookingShooking\">Twitter</a>,!", "serves": "2", "author": "Yaman Agarwal", "slug": "mirchi-sambharo-condiments-for-fried-food", "recipeIngredients": [{"group": {"name": "", "ingredients": [{"ingredient": "Onion", "quantity": "2 {finely chopped}"}, {"quantity": "1/4 cup", "ingredient": "Coconut"}, {"quantity": "1/4 cup {roughly diced}", "ingredient": "Potato"}, {"ingredient": "Carrots", "quantity": "1/4 cu